![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/cf9460c9-5bf8-4351-8735-35b77e691694/20240415_170400.jpg?format=original)

WWE RAW opens with Rhea Ripley announcing that she’s been benched for “quite a few months”. Rhea says she’s been told she needs to vacate the WWE Women's World Championship.

Massive “BULLSHIT” chants break out. “THANK YOU, MAMI” chants.

Rhea starts blaming Liv Morgan for this. Saying if she was a woman, she would’ve attacked Rhea head on.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/c8fb0981-40d5-4131-9345-4e0ed35676af/20240415_171138.jpg?format=original)

Rhea says if she finds Liv, she’s going to end up in jail for what she does to her. Liv doesn’t wait. Comes to confront Rhea but security would not let it happen

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/ce93a96c-403e-474a-a1a6-ab31b2de3b9d/Screenshot_20240415_171522.jpg?format=original)

Judgement Day says goodbye to Mami.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/f50e9046-7e9f-478a-ae8d-d37f84aeeb52/20240415_171715.jpg?format=original)

SHEAMUS RETURNS WITH HIS ORIGINAL THEME!!!

*   ## **_SHEAMUS def. IVAR_**
    

Sheamus and Ivar go out and do the damn thing. At one point, Sheamus hits an Avalanche White Noise for the sake of it. I love it. 10 more minutes and they could’ve had a really great match. Sheamus is using knee strikes now. Good match.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/a4a05d2a-41a5-4c35-bb6a-fa98b99740ae/20240415_173543.jpg?format=original)

Triple H makes an unannounced appearance to unveil a new Championship Belt or belts. It appears to be the WWE RAW Tag Team Championships.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/f95a475b-c5d7-49a2-8da4-b4f0a7cea9dc/20240415_173844.jpg?format=original)

WWE RAW and SMACKDOWN Tag Team titles are GONE.

Welcome back the WWE and World Tag Team Champions

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/c359f9b0-b300-42d6-9a0e-273f3c7c90e7/20240415_174129.jpg?format=original)

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/ab2e8ce4-05a8-46b2-8fa7-54fa76328e6f/20240415_175504.jpg?format=original)

A QR code quickly glitches on screen. Presumably for Uncle Howdy's return.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/78014725-a1f7-4e1f-8566-976abdb1d08d/20240415_175613.jpg?format=original)

*   ## **_#1 CONTENDERS MATCH FOR THE WORLD TAG TEAM CHAMPIONSHIPS: DIY def. NEW DAY and CREED BROS_**
    

Pretty good triple threat. Would have had a better atmosphere in front of a different crowd.

DIY will face their ReGeneration X partners for the World Tag Team Championships

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/8f222bee-e4a0-439d-9931-ca41f4b1c73b/20240415_180858.jpg?format=original)

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/0eb98822-2c5e-41bf-be38-fa8b6c0afdf7/Screenshot_20240415_181316.jpg?format=original)

Jackie Redmond attempts to interview Drew but he kicks over a light instead. Still angry about losing the World Championship.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/69f4a40e-2707-4d58-afe7-2667dc91bfdf/Screenshot_20240415_181814.jpg?format=original)

*   ## _CANDICE LERAE AND INDI HARTWELL DEF. IVY NILE AND MAXXINE DURPI_
    

Indi finally understands what Candice meant and she turns heel with her. They win their match thanks to heel tactics.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/d2e4d27f-eff0-4773-945b-da81f830aec1/20240415_182154.jpg?format=original)

Damian Priest takes charge of Judgement Day. Sends Dom to take care of Andrade tonight. Balor asks why he’s facing Jey Uso instead of trying to gain back their Tag Titles together. Priest says Balor needs to focus on tonight and teaching Jey Uso that he shouldn’t mess with the Judgement Day.

Balor looks pissed but he smiles. He understands… or does he?

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/1740763d-f078-4b84-a42f-2548febd456c/20240415_182728.jpg?format=original)

Jackie Redman does a cool interview with Chad Gable while he’s training earlier in the day. She asks Chad about the hometown crowd for Sami and he says it doesn’t bother him.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/35ddb684-0a89-43ba-92a1-f875526c9800/20240415_184000.jpg?format=original)

*   ## **_ANDRADE DEF. DOMINIK MYSTERIO_**
    

Pretty great match. Towards the end, Dom hits a Canadian Destroyer on the apron IN CANADA?!?!?!

JD and Dom jump Andrade until Ricochet comes out for the save.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/45b1487c-d4da-42a7-a676-49573b8bff5d/20240415_184609.jpg?format=original)

Cathy Kelly asks Jey Uso what he thinks about his brother Jimmy being jumped out of the Bloodline. Jey says the Bloodline is not a joke. He tried to get Jimmy out of there with him… He trails off.. Sad.

Tells Cathy it’s not time for this. It’s time to concentrate on Judgement Day, Finn Balor tonightand winning the World Title from Damian Priest.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/22e0029a-f608-458d-8c90-1c8771506872/20240415_185102.jpg?format=original)

*   ## **_CHELSEA GREEN AND PIPER NIVEN DEF. KATANA CHANCE AND KAYDEN CARTER_**
    

Nothing match. Glad Piper and Chrleas Green finally picked up a win.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/567b166c-a192-4faf-a420-ebc41eb5c38c/20240415_190138.jpg?format=original)

ITS OFFICIALLY THE WWE UNDISPUTED CHAMPIONSHIP. NO MORE UNIVERSAL.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/bc64b4bf-05a6-4c98-a171-98c52ef9f572/20240415_191407.jpg?format=original)

*   ## **_“Until we Yeet again…”_**
    

Cody Rhodes says he thinks The Rock has more matches in him and not just one.

“If I’m gonna bleed, youre gonna bleed with me.” - Cody Rhodes to The Rock

Cody Rhodes is here to inform the RAW audience that he is off to Smackdown to fulfill his duties as WWE Undisputed Champion

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/1f54c2cf-c051-409a-9bfe-ee58baeccdfc/20240415_192557.jpg?format=original)

*   ## **_JEY USO DEF. FINN BALOR_**
    

Quick match. The story is in the loss as Damian Priest is disappointed in Judgement Day for losing all night.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/b594b33d-7bdd-4ab2-a649-0a9d0e60ec53/20240415_192652.jpg?format=original)

What is next for the Judgement Day as tension continues to build between them?

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/937a14a7-e0e0-427c-a46d-cdf9ce6fb8b9/20240415_193012.jpg?format=original)

Sami Zayn tells Jey Uso that the first show he ever saw was in this building over 25 years ago.

He comes back as a champion and wants to walk through the front door like he did back then.

We follow Sami Zayn from the conversation with Jey Uso directly to his entrance without ever changing the camera in one of the very best entrances I’ve ever seen on Monday Night Raw.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/b25758cd-71d4-4c3e-9c95-b6c260bff768/20240415_193931.jpg?format=original)

New Women’s World Champion NEXT WEEK?!

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/276a0ebd-441b-4800-86c7-2f3a9ed5663f/20240415_194246.jpg?format=original)

*   ## **_INTERCONTINENTAL CHAMPIONSHIP: SAMI ZAYN(c) def CHAD GABLE_**
    

Heavy boos for Chad Gable to kick this off. Excellent pro wrestling match between these gents. Would love to see one more heated match with a stip.

Chad Gable turns on Sami Zayn by German Suplexing him RIGHT OUT OF HIS WIFE'S ARMS. PERFECT CLOSE TO THIS RAW AS GABLE TAKES OUT HIS FRUSTRATION ON SAMI ZAYN FOR THE NEXT 2 MINUTES.